    "bio": "Product Led Growth at Superchat, the customer communication platform where teams stay in the loop on what their AI and workflows are doing. I build automation workflows that connect AI, WhatsApp, and business tools to help companies communicate smarter and faster. On TikTok and Instagram (@springertogrow), I share entertaining and useful workflows. These n8n templates are battle-tested solutions our customers use.",
    "verified": false,
